AHOY! I'm the Dread Pirate Roberts, and I have a secret!
It is a number from 1 to 99. I'll give you 6 tries.
What's yer guess? 40
Too high, landlubber!
What's yer guess? 20
Too high, landlubber!
What's yer guess? 10
Too low, ye scurvy dog!
What's yer guess? 11
Too low, ye scurvy dog!
What's yer guess? 12
Avast! Ye got it! Found my secret, ye did!